{"story":{"group_1":[{"armatureList":[{"animation":["action"],"armatureId":1,"filePath":"resource/image_native/effect/story/general/3507_film_frame.ExportJson","zOrder":"messageBack"}],"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_20191.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":200906,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200501,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"item":[{"anchor":"skip","path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/mt_calender_day-xx.png","posX":-4,"posY":-50,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"messageFront"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm01_anime07","chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200906,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-001-1"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Two fair young maidens,@alone in such a secluded place...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnFirst":3.6,"autoTurnNoDelay":1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":200906,"voiceFull":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-001-2"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]What are they about to do, as they@gaze into each other's eyes...?!"},{"chara":[{"id":200906,"motion":400}]},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200501,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-001-3","voiceFullStop":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-001-2"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Yes, yes. Enough of that."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":200501,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-001-4"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Now go ahead and look into@today's forecast."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200906,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-001-5"},{"id":200501,"motion":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Oh, you're spoiling the mood..."},{"chara":[{"id":200906,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-001-6"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]When we first started off, you used to show@a bit more hesitation and embarrassment."},{"chara":[{"id":200906,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-001-7"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]But now, you're just dryly using this@as a convenient tool for Witch hunting..."},{"chara":[{"id":200906,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-001-8"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Is this what they call@the post-honeymoon period?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":200501,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-001-9"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Oh, so you want to spice things up? There's@always the option to head into battle..."},{"chara":[{"id":200906,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-001-10"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Nope. No thanks!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200906,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-001-11"},{"id":200501,"motion":1}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I mean, this is fine.@But like..."},{"chara":[{"id":200906,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-001-12"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Is it really okay for ordinary life@to go on like this forever...?"},{"autoTurnFirst":2.1,"autoTurnNoDelay":1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200906,"voiceFull":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-001-13"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]It's probably fine...@Yeah..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200906}]},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":200906,"motion":400,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-001-14","voiceFullStop":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-001-13"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]So, the verdict is:@No problem at all!"},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-001-15"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Mabayu."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200906,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-001-16"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]What?"},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"autoTurnNoDelay":1,"chara":[{"id":200501,"motion":300,"voiceFull":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-001-17"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]You really are a little...different."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200501}]},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":200906,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-001-18","voiceFullStop":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-001-17"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Heh heh heh.@I am, aren't I?!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200906,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-001-19"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]That's why I don't have many friends."},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-001-20"},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":200906,"motion":0}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Honestly, having lots of friends doesn't@mean much if the bond between you is shallow."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200501,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-001-21"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]It's a very precious thing to have@even one trustworthy friend."},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-001-22"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Especially for Magical Girls like us."},{"chara":[{"id":200906,"lipSynch":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-001-23"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]......"},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-001-24"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Now then. Let's go about protecting@the town for today, Miss Strategist."},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"textAvClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"effect":"ef_adv_05","face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":200900,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"se":"7205_magic_girl"},{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"autoTurnNoDelay":1,"chara":[{"id":200900,"voiceFull":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-001-25"},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":200501,"motion":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Y-yeah.@Then, let me go ahead and..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":200900}]},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"black","bgm":"stop","item":[{"anchor":"skip","path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/mt_calender_day-xx.png","posX":-4,"posY":-50,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"messageFront"},{"path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/film13_mami_seriously.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"charaFront"}],"textAvClear":1,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","voiceFullStop":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913006-001-25"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"white","deleteArmatureList":[1],"item":[{"anchor":"skip","path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/mt_calender_day-xx.png","posX":-4,"posY":-50,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"messageFront"}],"turnChangeIn":"whiteIn"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"turnChangeOut":"whiteOut","turnChangeOutTime":0.1},{"armatureList":[{"animation":["action"],"armatureId":1,"filePath":"resource/image_native/effect/story/general/3507_fil